title: Ghost In The Shell Manga Complete
description:
The original Ghost in the Shell, Man Machine Interface, and Human Error Processor mangas by Shirow Masamune.  If there's any problems, comments, or questions, feel free to message me.

I couldn't find a complete GITS manga collection torrent anywhere, so I created one.  Maybe I didn't look hard enough, but hell, might as well have another if there is already one.

Also, goddamn shortened name, should be Malaikvavit.
